\subsection{Method \code{draw()}}{
Draw non-centromeric bands with \code{grid::grid.rect()} and
centromere triangles with \code{grid::grid.polygon()}. With
\code{style = "rounded"}, the leftmost / rightmost bands draw with
rounded telomere caps. With \code{scope = "full"}, the current window
region is overlaid as a highlight rectangle.
